This paper discusses the use of natural language processing techniques for biomedical event extraction, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for this task, which is relevant to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE).
